HEADWORD: high road
<hw>high road</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The most ethical and honest
method; -- used mostly in the phrase to <ex>take the high road</ex> (as
in an election campaign). Contrasted with <ex>low road</ex>.</def>⟦br⟧
